@uri = http://localhost:9004/api/v1/settlements

### Get all settlements - Default (paginated)
GET {{uri}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Get all settlements - With pagination
GET {{uri}}?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Get all settlements - With sorting
GET {{uri}}?sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Filter settlements - Search by keyword (matches jobContent, address, note)
GET {{uri}}/filter?search=road
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Filter settlements - By status
GET {{uri}}/filter?status=APPROVED
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Filter settlements - By multiple statuses
GET {{uri}}/filter?status=APPROVED&status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Filter settlements - By registration date range
GET {{uri}}/filter?registrationFrom=2026-01-01&registrationTo=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Filter settlements - By connection fee range
GET {{uri}}/filter?connectionFeeMin=1000000&connectionFeeMax=5000000
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Filter settlements - By creation date range
GET {{uri}}/filter?createdAtFrom=2026-01-01T00:00:00&createdAtTo=2026-12-31T23:59:59
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Filter settlements - Combined filters (search + status + date range)
GET {{uri}}/filter?search=construction&status=APPROVED&registrationFrom=2026-01-01&connectionFeeMin=2000000
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Filter settlements - With pagination and sorting
GET {{uri}}/filter?search=road&page=0&size=5&sort=registrationAt,asc
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Filter settlements - Empty search
GET {{uri}}/filter?search=
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Filter settlements - Invalid date format (should return 400)
GET {{uri}}/filter?registrationFrom=invalid-date
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Filter settlements - connectionFeeMin > connectionFeeMax (should return 400)
GET {{uri}}/filter?connectionFeeMin=5000000&connectionFeeMax=1000000
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Get settlement by ID
GET {{uri}}/5513e1e5-a627-440a-be72-a84aa1315fc6
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Create settlement - Happy case
POST {{uri}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "jobContent": "Xây dựng đường giao thông",
  "address": "123 Đường ABC, Phường X, Quận Y",
  "connectionFee": 2500000,
  "note": "Khách hàng yêu cầu hoàn thành trước Tết",
  "status": "PENDING",
  "registrationAt": "2026-03-15"
}

### Create settlement - Missing required fields
POST {{uri}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "jobContent": "",
  "address": "",
  "connectionFee": -100000
}

