### Update settlement - Happy case
PUT {{uri}}/5513e1e5-a627-440a-be72-a84aa1315fc6
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "jobContent": "Cập nhật nội dung công trình",
  "address": "456 Đường XYZ, Phường X, Quận Y",
  "connectionFee": 3000000,
  "note": "Cập nhật ghi chú",
  "status": "APPROVED",
  "registrationAt": "2026-03-18"
}

### Update settlement - Not found
PUT {{uri}}/invalid-id
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "jobContent": "Test",
  "address": "Test",
  "connectionFee": 1000000
}

### Delete settlement - Happy case
DELETE {{uri}}/5513e1e5-a627-440a-be72-a84aa1315fc6
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Delete settlement - Not found
DELETE {{uri}}/invalid-id
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json
